I wish we'd gone to Brooklyn sooner.

262
00:13:50,157 --> 00:13:51,537
I know, right?

263
00:13:51,703 --> 00:13:53,720
Ever since the Trader Joe's
opened up,

264
00:13:53,845 --> 00:13:55,916
Brooklyn is so... whatever.

265
00:13:57,027 --> 00:13:58,419
Wait. Where'd you get that?

266
00:13:58,585 --> 00:13:59,712
Across the street

267
00:13:59,878 --> 00:14:01,378
at the Intersection.

268
00:14:03,288 --> 00:14:04,304
So...

269
00:14:05,308 --> 00:14:06,358
You guys...

270
00:14:07,311 --> 00:14:09,013
wanna buy some weed or...?

271
00:14:18,715 --> 00:14:21,743
