of every interview for your questions.

291
00:15:22,157 --> 00:15:23,292
So don't hold back.

292
00:15:23,417 --> 00:15:25,879
Whatever you got inside there,
you just let her rip.

293
00:15:27,797 --> 00:15:29,395
<i>I can't do this anymore.</i>

294
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:31,218
<i>I'm just gonna tell him the truth.</i>

295
00:15:33,039 --> 00:15:35,712
When it's stomach stuff,
you just say "Under the weather"

296
00:15:35,837 --> 00:15:39,137
or people start picturing you
doing unspeakable things.

297
00:15:40,334 --> 00:15:42,948
I have food poisoning
and I'm about to start volcanoing

298
00:15:43,073 --> 00:15:44,932
toxic sludge out of both ends!

299
00:15:45,057 --> 00:15:46,066
Nailed it.

300
00:15:49,930 --> 00:15:51,130
Thanks, Julia!

301
00:15:53,876 --> 00:15:55,476
No, on second thought.

302
00:15:57,805 --> 00:15:59,413
- Come on.
- What the hell?!

303
00:15:59,579 --> 00:16:02,124
You can't get back with Zoey
over a lightbulb.

304
00:16:02,290 --> 00:16:04,293
I'm not freaking out
over a lightbulb!

305
00:16:04,459 --> 00:16:07,009
I'm freaking out over
50,000 lightbulbs!

306
00:16:07,309 --> 00:16:08,609
I can't do this!

307
00:16:09,047 --> 00:16:11,425
I only got this job because
you gave it to me, Barney.

308
00:16:11,591 --> 00:16:12,941
I didn't earn it!

309
00:16:15,891 --> 00:16:17,391
The future is scary.

310
00:16:17,715 --> 00:16:21,226
But you can't just run back to the past
because it's familiar.

311
00:16:22,602 --> 00:16:24,052
Yes, it's tempting.

312
00:16:25,706 --> 00:16:26,707
But...

313
00:16:27,551 --> 00:16:28,801
It's a mistake.

314
00:16:32,231 --> 00:16:33,381
You're right.

315
00:16:35,561 --> 00:16:36,562
Excuse me.

316
00:16:37,241 --> 00:16:39,953
Can you give this to the blonde
sitting alone in there

317
00:16:40,531 --> 00:16:42,914
and tell her Ted's really sorry?

318
00:16:44,079 --> 00:16:45,208
Also...

319
00:16:46,690 --> 00:16:49,713
Indirect sunlight. Don't overwater.
Half a cup a week is more than enough.

320
00:17:07,021 --> 00:17:08,071
<i>And kids...</i>

321
00:17:10,441 --> 00:17:12,391
