322
00:17:13,350 --> 00:17:15,350
<i>Psych. It was just some chick.</i>

323
00:17:19,779 --> 00:17:21,078
Hey, baby, how'd it go?

324
00:17:21,244 --> 00:17:22,544
Lily, this year,

325
00:17:23,032 --> 00:17:25,793
this nasty schoolyard bully of a year

326
00:17:25,918 --> 00:17:27,918
will not stop punching me
in the face.

327
00:17:28,439 --> 00:17:30,565
How did we kick off 2011?

328
00:17:30,690 --> 00:17:32,005
My dad died.

329
00:17:32,171 --> 00:17:34,522
And now after five months
of unemployment,

330
00:17:34,647 --> 00:17:35,968
I just blew my dream job.

331
00:17:36,134 --> 00:17:39,342
The good news is, in a few seconds,
I'm gonna start heaving my guts out

332
00:17:39,467 --> 00:17:41,542
because that's what life is
for me now,

333
00:17:41,667 --> 00:17:44,685
just losing what's inside
until I'm just empty.

334
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,186
Baby, come here.

335
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:50,524
I just want to shut my eyes
for a few seconds before it starts.

336
00:18:01,566 --> 00:18:03,113
<i>And Marshall slept...</i>

337
00:18:06,964 --> 00:18:07,999
<i>... all night.</i>

338
00:18:23,890 --> 00:18:25,225
Who's gonna do the honors?

339
00:18:26,423 --> 00:18:27,436
He is.

340
00:18:27,810 --> 00:18:28,812
You sure?

341
00:18:30,305 --> 00:18:31,314
You earned it.

342
00:18:34,166 --> 00:18:35,167
All clear!

343
00:18:39,780 --> 00:18:41,241
New is always better, right?

344
00:18:42,387 --> 00:18:43,493
Always.

345
00:18:45,369 --> 00:18:46,370
Ten,

346
00:18:46,659 --> 00:18:48,415
nine, eight...

347
00:18:50,514 --> 00:18:52,562
It's a miracle.
I didn't get sick.

348
00:18:52,687 --> 00:18:54,296
I didn't get sick.

349
00:18:54,918 --> 00:18:56,068
I know, baby.

350
00:18:57,987 --> 00:18:59,137
I'm pregnant.

351
00:19:34,335 --> 00:19:36,421
I'm proud of you
for giving Ted the button.

352
00:19:37,207 --> 00:19:38,457
It meant a lot.

353
00:19:38,582 --> 00:19:39,886
It's just a button.

354
00:19:40,011 --> 00:19:42,611
Can we talk about
something else, please?

355
00:19:50,888 --> 00:19:51,895
How you been?

356
00:19:52,433 --> 00:19:53,438
Fine.

357
00:19:56,941 --> 00:20:00,136
I don't know why you would possibly
say yes to this, but,

358
00:20:00,579 --> 00:20:02,989
